34 public:
35 FlexfecReceiveStreamImpl(
36 Clock* clock,
37 RtpStreamReceiverControllerInterface* receiver_controller,

41 ProcessThread* process_thread);

53

57 // RTCP reporting.
58 const std::unique_ptr<ReceiveStatistics> rtp_receive_statistics_;
59 const std::unique_ptr<ModuleRtpRtcpImpl2> rtp_rtcp_;
60 ProcessThread* process_thread_;
